sedutil for Debian

The sedutil Debian package provides the sedutil-cli in /usr/sbin
and the scripts to create the PBA for the passphrase input as 
buildPBAscripts.tar.gz in /usr/share/doc/sedutil.

Also the sysctl config libata.allow_tpm is enabled.

